Average per team per season
GET /api/aggregates/teams/{teamId}?season=2024

Response JSON example:

{
    "teamId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "season": 2025,
    "avgPoints": 30.0,
    "avgRebounds": 10.0,
    "avgAssists": 8.0,
    "avgSteals": 2.0,
    "avgBlocks": 1.0,
    "avgFouls": 2.0,
    "avgTurnovers": 3.0,
    "avgMinutesPlayed": 40.0
}
